headline: Republic Services Certified as a Great Place to Work® for Ninth Consecutive Year
summary: Republic Services, Inc. (NYSE: RSG), a leader in the environmental services industry, has been certified as a Great Place to Work® for a ninth consecutive time. The recognition, awarded by the global authority on workplace culture and employee experience, is based on direct feedback from employees about their workplace experiences.
